<p>
<p>You bought two lottery tickets. The first X has a profit expectation of € 0.60 with a standard deviation of € 0.75 and the second Y has € 0.75 profit expectation with € 0.32 standard deviation. If you exclude the cost of the lots, what is your expectation value of the total profit and its standard deviation?</p>
</p>]]></text>
